txt.en: Dûn Traikh is in western Elderslade.\n\nYou should destroy the black powder crates in Dûn Traikh.
Gunvald is in Annâk-khurfu, in eastern Elderslade.\n\nYou should talk to Gunvald.
Destroyed black powder crates in Dûn Traikh ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

'The Angmarim have gotten themselves quite comfortably set up near the walls of Gundabad. Our scouts inform me that stockpiles of black powder are all over the town of Dûn Traikh. If we can hit these stores before we begin our major assault, it will be a solid blow to the enemy.'
The Angmarim town of Dûn Traikh holds dangerous stores of foul black powder.
'Well done, friend. You have saved lives and helped the war effort immensely with this deed.'
